     C                     MOVE '99'      @@ID
JW4   * F7: PRINT DCL LIST  ------------------
 |   C           *INKG     WHEQ *ON
 |   C                     CALL 'AB#C5M'
JW4  C                     MOVE MSG,11    D@MSG
      * F9: INQ -----------------------------
     C           *INKI     WHEQ *ON
     C                     EXSR #SET
     C           RRN1      IFGT *ZERO
     C                     MOVE '03'      @@ID
