JW1   * F10: ORDER INQ ----------------------
 |   C           *INKJ     WHEQ *ON
 |   C                     CALL 'AB#R1F'
 |   C                     PARM           D@PRT1
 |   C                     PARM           D@PRT2
 |   C                     PARM           D@PRT3
 |   C                     PARM           D@PRT4
JW1  C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C                     OTHER
